song_lyrics: Juo shobhānidhi Ghanshyām, mūrti manmā game,
Bhāve bhāḷī manohar māv, muni keḍe bhame... Juo
Shir bāndhī sonerī pāgh, pech zūkyā pāpaṇe,
Man levā laṭkāḷo lā:, tore motīḍā taṇe... Juo
Mukhe bole madhurā veṇ, vadhāre vahālne,
Lajjā pāme koṭik kām, bhāḷī Hari bhālne... Juo
Tan tej dekhī prakāsh, ghaṭe ravi chandanā,
Evā shobhe sundar Shyām, vālo Dayānandnā... Juo
title: Juo shobhānidhi Ghanshyām mūrti manmā game
